PN,38501
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,FA doctor who called for an
OL,7,Finvestigation into the safety of the
OL,8,FCOVID-19 vaccine has been sacked by
OL,9,FGuernsey's Medical Specialist Group
OL,10,F(MSG).
OL,12,FConsultant cardiologist Dr Dean
OL,13,FPatterson has not been involved in
OL,14,Fpatient care with the group since
OL,15,FFebruary 2025 and, after an
OL,16,Finvestigation, the organisation
OL,17,Fannounced that Dr Patterson has been
OL,18,Fdismissed.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,FThe MSG has not made the reason for
OL,7,Fthis decision public but says:
OL,8,F"Following the conclusion of our
OL,9,Finternal processes, we can confirm
OL,10,Fthat as of 19 March 2026, Dr Dean
OL,11,FPatterson is no longer a partner at
OL,12,Fthe Medical Specialist Group."
OL,14,FIn the aftermath of the COVID-19
OL,15,Fpandemic, he said he wanted to open a
OL,16,Fdebate about a possible link between
OL,17,Fincreased cases of myocarditis -
OL,18,Finflammation of the heart - following
OL,19,Fthe vaccination rollout.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,FDr Patterson pointed to a jump in
OL,7,Fcases of this condition in Guernsey,
OL,8,Frising from five in 2020 to 25 the
OL,9,Ffollowing year and remaining at a
OL,10,Fhigher level of 22 incidences in 2022.
OL,12,FThis dropped in 2023, when fewer
OL,13,Fvaccines were given.
OL,15,FSpeaking to ITV Channel in 2024, he
OL,16,Fsaid: "People think I must have come
OL,17,Fto this conclusion just like that, but
OL,18,FI haven't.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,F"It's been running on guts, instinct
OL,7,Fat first, not being quite happy,
OL,8,Ftrying to speak to people, then hoping
OL,9,Fto prove myself wrong.
OL,11,F"I think the scientific debate has
OL,12,Fbeen stifled. People and doctors have
OL,13,Fbeen threatened and lost their jobs,
OL,14,FI've had nursing staff at the hospital
OL,15,Fcontact me and say they can't speak
OL,16,Fout because of disciplinaries."
OL,18,FDr Patterson insisted that he is not
OL,19,Fan "anti-vaxxer".
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,FBoth Guernsey's Health and Social Care
OL,7,Fdepartment and the MSG were quick to
OL,8,Fdistance themselves from these
OL,9,Fcomments, insisting that the benefits
OL,10,Fof the vaccination far outweighed any
OL,11,Fpossible side effects.
OL,13,FIn response to Dr Patterson's
OL,14,Fconcerns, the States of Guernsey
OL,15,Fcommissioned an independent review by
OL,16,Fthe Royal College of Physicians at the
OL,17,Fend of 2024 to investigate the claims.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,FA spokesperson from the MSG says: "The
OL,7,Freview found no evidence to support
OL,8,Fthe level of clinical concerns raised
OL,9,Fby Dr Patterson.
OL,11,F"However, as a result of certain
OL,12,Fissues identified by the Royal College
OL,13,Fas part of the review, further
OL,14,Finvestigations were undertaken by the
OL,15,FMedical Specialist Group in the
OL,16,Finterests of the safety of our
OL,17,Fpatients."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,FIt is not clear what those concerns
OL,7,Fwere, but in February 2026, Dr
OL,8,FPatterson was suspended from
OL,9,Fpractising for a year by the
OL,10,Findependent General Medical Council
OL,11,F(GMC), which regulates doctors.
OL,13,FThis is an interim order while the
OL,14,FCouncil investigates his fitness to
OL,15,Fpractice and Dr Patterson is appealing
OL,16,Fhis suspension.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,FThe MSG spokesperson says that
OL,7,FGuernsey's cardiology service "runs as
OL,8,Fnormal by other colleagues within the
OL,9,Fteam and by experienced visiting
OL,10,Fconsultants", while it has "written
OL,11,Fdirectly to patients who may have been
OL,12,Faffected by this process".
OL,14,FThe spokesperson adds: "Every decision
OL,15,Fwe have taken throughout this process
OL,16,Fhas been focused on ensuring the
OL,17,Fhighest standards of patient care.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,386,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F385A1774638671
OL,3,CDoctor who questioned COVID-19 vaccine
OL,4,Cside effects sacked
OL,6,F"The investigation by the GMC is
OL,7,Fongoing, and it is important that this
OL,8,Fprocess is allowed to run its proper
OL,9,Fcourse."
OL,11,FThe MSG says anyone with questions or
OL,12,Fconcerns about their care by Dr
OL,13,FPatterson can contact them directly by
OL,14,Femailing customercare@msg.gg or
OL,15,Fcalling 01481 238565 and they will
OL,16,Freview it.
OL,18,FMore health news from Guernsey:
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G9/10
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
